Second Department,

November, 1959 *

(November 30, 1959) Morris Lorberblatt, Appellant, v. D. A. Gerst, Inc., Respondent.

Motion to vacate order entered October 5, 1959, dismissing appeal, and for other relief denied, without costs. Present — Wenzel, Acting P. J., Beldock, Hallinan and Kleinfeld, JJ.; Murphy, J., deceased.
